==Useful Info==
'''Chuck''' is a [[unique]] [[stone giant]] found only in the [[Dungeon Sprint]] map, [[The Ten Rune Challenge]]. Although not much beefier than a standard stone giant, he is a crack shot with his [[large rock]]s of [[chaos]].

==Tips & Tricks==
*Every time a chaos-branded large rock hits you, there's a (very small) chance for you to be [[paralysed]] for 5 turns and immediately die. At the very least, Chuck won't fire rocks past other monsters.

==History==
*When monsters gained infinite ammo in [[0.27]], Chuck's rock of [[returning]] was replaced with chaos.
